{"tid":1500691,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"是但哥整理的白宮聯署更新","createTime":"2019-08-24T06:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T17:03:24.000Z","uid":258680,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"8aebae356e47e22aa07cff96720aa8045965b434","tid":1500691,"uid":258680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:04:54.000Z","msg":"【現存白宮聯署更新】<br />\n<br />\n明白現在實在太多白宮聯署，好多人會唔記得自己簽咗邊個，我有以下建議：<br />\n<br />\n1/ 唔肯定嘅，簽多一次。在我的道德標準下，呢個可以，因為你唔係故意用同一個電郵簽幾次。<br />\n<br />\n2/ 簽咗之後，自己mark返自己簽咗邊個，這是大家的責任。<br />\n<br />\n《未夠數》<br />\n==========<br />\n中國武警冒充香港警察，白宮聯署請求美國國會盡快通過香港人權民主法案 <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2YW8pa8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2YW8pa8&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=8ecff53a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2YW8pa8</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國取消中國學生簽證<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/30GcBMM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F30GcBMM&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=b4531df0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/30GcBMM</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國派美軍拯救香港巿民<br />\n <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KsmYOQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KsmYOQ&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=3fc77f8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KsmYOQ</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國將中國共產黨定性為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MlpLM3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MlpLM3&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=2c1aafcf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MlpLM3</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國向北京施壓，停止製造白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Zkc8hX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Zkc8hX&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=5d9bac2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Zkc8hX</a><br />\n<br />\n拯救國泰航空，保障經濟自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZmWgPU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZmWgPU&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=ca2e30ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZmWgPU</a><br />\n<br />\n要求拒絕前警務處處長曾偉雄到聯合國就任提名<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Z0cMkw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Z0cMkw&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=497f9b52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Z0cMkw</a><br />\n🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸<br />\n《以下夠數，但到期前越多人越好》<br />\n==========<br />\n請求美國派出醫療船支援香港 <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2H221Iu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2H221Iu&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=1d9e239c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2H221Iu</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國國會確認香港警察為恐怖組織 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KzVVQB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KzVVQB&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=69ee011a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KzVVQB</a><br />\n<br />\n請美國國會提名【爭取民主自由的香港人】競逐諾貝爾和平獎，藉以保護義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZbGdQH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZbGdQH&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=e4f955d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZbGdQH</a><br />\n<br />\n簽名＞等電郵＞確認簽名＞傳開去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原link<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2373594089374391&amp;id=764219590311857\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2373594089374391%26id%3D764219590311857&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=8cc166b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2373594089374391&amp;id=764219590311857</a>"},{"pid":"0eeb1f802b0645ff2deeb1cde994f2e9690443b9","tid":1500691,"uid":258680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:12:24.000Z","msg":"幫手推！<br />\n<i